先看/bkup路由

```javascript
app.put('/bkup', (req, res) => {
  let date_stream = Buffer.from(JSON.stringify(date)); 
  const cmd = ba.redis_set + `date ${date_stream.toString('base64')}`;
  exec(cmd, (err,_,__) => {
